gg_extreme_office_v1

Very small office like map designed for very fast paced gungame play.

20 spawns (10 Terrorist, 10 Counter Terrorist)

No .nav as of yet (Sorry) working on that in a later release(v2 will have models and a cube map as well as bot navigation).

Later release of this map will have some added rooms for cs_, or, de_ play(and also still have a gg_ version) .
